HEADWORD: Connotative
<hw>Con*no"ta*tive</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocr⟧n*n⟦omac⟧"t⟦adot⟧*t⟦icr⟧v ⟦or⟧
k⟦ocr⟧n"n⟦osl⟧*t⟦asl⟧*t⟦icr⟧v)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
